<br>
I would prefer you lower the stats on some items.  All/All or monk only as opposed to nerfing the base defense of a monk.  Just dont remove monk from the useable class on an item.  It would be hard to equip a few slots overnight with reasonable gear.<br>
<br>
While I may have passed that point in the game I think it would be a shame to hurt the pre 60 monks with casual gear.<br>
<br>
If this nerf is only targeted at the high end monk then institute a cap and tell us what it is.  We will complain less.  <br>
<br>
My rogue dinged 37 today... preparing for the nerf to be so bad I dont want to be a monk anymore.   I'm not sure I have the energy to level another class to 60+.  Please don't weaken or change the role of the one I love to a degree that I would consider finding an alternative.<br>
